article.description: — Ty Gordon had 30 points as Nicholls State won its eighth straight game, getting past Northwestern State 80-62 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Gordon carries Nicholls St. past Northwestern St. 80-62
article.linkText: Gordon carries Nicholls St. past Northwestern St. 80-62
article.story: NATCHITOCHES, La. -- — Ty Gordon had 30 points as Nicholls State won its eighth straight game, getting past Northwestern State 80-62 on Thursday night. Latrell Jones had 19 points and 10 rebounds for Nicholls State (19-9, 11-3 Southland Conference). Devante Carter added 13 points, seven rebounds and seven assists. Kendal Coleman had 19 points and 13 rebounds for the Demons (8-21, 5-10). Carvell Teasett, the Demons' second leading scorer coming into the matchup at 10 points per game, was held to only five points on 2-of-13 shooting. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
